Reasoning: The paper deals with text recognition in scanned documents, which is a problem in computer vision (cs.CV). It also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as the text needs to be processed and understood. The use of open-source packages suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and the evaluation of the proposed method involves the use of a database, which could fall under data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
